general%20intelligence%20and%20routes%20tasks%20to%20the%20right%20model%20to%20improve%20user%20experience.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BIt%20makes%20that%20decision%20for%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20OpenAI%20COO%20Brad%20Lightcap%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20AI%20industry%20is%20always%20talking%20about%20breakthroughs%20in%20intelligence%20and%20benchmark%20wins%2C%20but%20the%20biggest%20story%20this%20week%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgpt5-free-chatgpt-openai-sam-altman-agi-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGPT-5%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20and%20how%20easy%20it%20is%20to%20use%20for%20casual%20users%20not%20paying%20attention%20to%20every%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20promotes%20the%20new%20and%20improved%20capabilities%20of%20every%20iteration%20of%20its%20flagship%20model.%20When%20OpenAI%20released%20GPT-4%2C%20it%20said%20the%20model%20%26quot%3Bexhibits%20human-level%20performance%20on%20various%20professional%20and%20academic%20benchmarks.%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-sam-altman-releases-gpt-4-5-emotionally-intelligent-model-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGPT-4.5%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20improved%20the%20model's%20%26quot%3Bability%20to%20recognize%20patterns%2C%20draw%20connections%2C%20and%20generate%20creative%20insights%20without%20reasoning.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGPT-5%2C%20OpenAI%20said%20on%20Thursday%2C%20marks%20%26quot%3Ba%20significant%20leap%20in%20intelligence%20over%20all%20our%20previous%20models%2C%20featuring%20state-of-the-art%20performance%20across%20coding%2C%20math%2C%20writing%2C%20health%2C%20visual%20perception%2C%20and%20more.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20one%20of%20the%20features%20OpenAI%20executives%20%E2%80%94%20and%20AI%20experts%20%E2%80%94%20are%20most%20excited%20about%20is%20what%20OpenAI%20calls%20a%20%26quot%3Breal-time%20router%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20system%20that%20selects%20the%20most%2