h%20the%20owner's%20manual%20for%20instructions%20as%20the%20sun%20began%20to%20set%20and%20a%20sense%20of%20unease%20started%20to%20settle%20over%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20were%20still%20hours%20away%20from%20our%20destination%20and%20didn't%20have%20the%20money%20for%20a%20place%20to%20stay%20if%20I%20couldn't%20get%20the%20tire%20sorted%20out.%20I%20turned%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fhow-to-jump-a-car%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehazard%20lights%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20started%20to%20fumble%20around%20in%20the%20trunk%20for%20the%20spare%20and%20the%20jack.%20Just%20as%20I%20was%20about%20to%20pull%20the%20tools%20out%2C%20I%20looked%20up%20and%20saw%20an%20old%20pickup%20truck%20idling%20in%20front%20of%20our%20car.%20A%20man%20hopped%20out%20of%20the%20driver's%20side%20and%20made%20his%20way%20over%20to%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ee367930-2575-428a-a9eb-446d399f399c%5C%22%3EI%20was%20completely%20caught%20off%20guard%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWithin%20moments%2C%20the%20man%20%E2%80%94%20without%20introduction%20or%20any%20small%20talk%20%E2%80%94%20asked%20for%20the%20tools%20and%20set%20to%20work.%20He%20talked%20through%20the%20entire%20process%20from%20setting%20the%20jack%20to%20loosening%20the%20bolts%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-change-a-tire-more-2017-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebefore%20removing%20the%20flat%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20a%20lifesaver.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20he%20did%20in%20minutes%20would%20likely%20have%20taken%20me%20an%20hour%20(minimum).%20I%20helped%20him%20pull%20the%20old%20tire%20off%2C%20rolled%20the%20new%20one%20over%2C%20and%20helped%20finalize%20the%20process.%20The%20gentleman%20had%20me%20tighten%20some%20of%20the%20bolts%20on%20the%20spare%20just%20to%20get%20a%20sense%20of%20what%20it%20felt%20like%20to%20do%20it%20myself%2C%20and%20then%20checked%20my%20work%20before%20tightening%20the%20rest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a70962b9-3775-4610-8609-34b44825db94%5C%22%3EAs%20quickly%20as%20he%20had%20arrived%2C%20he%20was%20gone%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20already%20feeling%20a%20very%20deep%20sense%20of%20gratitude%20toward%20our%20%26quot%3Broadside%20savior%26quot%3B%20and%2C%20as%20I%20put%20away%20the%20jack%2C%20started%20planning%20out%20my%20thank-you%20speech.%20My%20partner%20watched%20nearby%20as%20I%20heaved%20the%20flat%20into%20the%20trunk%20and%20finally%20slammed%20the%20lid%20closed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20opened%20my%20mouth%20to%20begin%20gushing%20out%20thanks%2C%20my%20partner%20and%20I%20realized%20simultaneously%20that%20the%20man%20was%20gone%20%E2%80%94%20truck%20and%20all.%20We%20didn't%20hear%20him%20get%20in%2C%20close%20the%20door%2C%20or%20drive%20away%20down%20the%20service%20road.%20It%20seemed%20impossible%20that%20he%20could%20have%20left%20as%20quickly%20as%20he%20did%2C%20and%20even%20less%20likely%20that%20neither%20of%20us%20wouldn't%20have%20noticed%20or%20heard%20his%20departure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20stood%20in%20awe%20of%20the%20unlikely%20moment%20we%20found%20ourselves%20in%20and%20looked%20at%20each%20other%2C%20speechless.%20This%20wasn't%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdifference-driving-in-the-us-and-france-2016-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Echaracteristic%20of%20the%20US%3C%2Fa%3E%20we%20were%20taught%20to%20believe%20in%2C%20where%20people%20were%20robbed%20or%20harmed%20on%20the%20side%20of%20the%20road%20in%20situations%20such%20as%20these.%20Nevertheless%2C%20we%20were%20able%20to%20get%20in%20our%20car%20and%20make%20it%20to%20the%20nearest%20town%20just%20in%20time%20to%20find%20a%20new%20tire%20and%20be%20on%20our%20way%20back%20to%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226872c0f5-198a-41dd-a0a3-683801ca499b%5C%22%3EThe%20care%20from%20a%20stranger%20caused%20me%20to%20reflect%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20fact%2C%20I%20spent%20considerable%20time%20reflecting%20on%20what%20that%20episode%20meant%20for%20the%20way%20I%20see%20others.%20I%20look%20back%20now%20and%20see%20how%20small%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-research-shows-women-are-more-generous-than-men-2017-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emoments%20of%20generosity%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20helped%20form%20my%20worldview%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20I%20was%20apprehensive%20and%20unsure%20of%20how%20to%20accept%20the%20help%20I%20received%20from%20a%20stranger%2C%20and%2C%20if%20I'm%20honest%2C%20I%20experienced%20some%20fear%20when%20he%20pulled%20up%20out%20of%20the%20blue.%20However%2C%20my%20initial%20judgment%20of%20the%20situation%20proved%20incorrect%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Facts-of-kindness-2019-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ekindness%20of%20our%20unknown%20friend's%20gesture%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20had%20to%20take%20some%20time%20to%20think%20about%20my%20own%20response%20to%20people%20whom%20I%20might%20encounter%20who%20could%20be%20going%20through%20a%20similar%20struggle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224a697056-79e0-431f-ba47-c07e06921740%5C%22%3ESingle%20moments%20can%20deeply%20impact%20others%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20know%20I%20will%20never%20get%20to%20thank%20our%20%26quot%3Bangel%20in%20a%20pickup%20truck%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20I%20hope%20some%20of%20my%20own%20opportunities%20to%20help%20in%20times%20of%20need%20have%20been%20the%20thank-you%20I%20would%20have%20given%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20moment%2C%20and%20others%20like%20it%2C%20have%20caused%20me%20to%20try%20to%20adopt%20a%20posture%20of%20what%20some%20call%20%26quot%3Bradical%20hospitality%26quot%3B.%20We%20are%20all%20affected%20by%20an%20accumulation%20of%20moments%20that%20we%20string%20together%20to%20form%20who%20we%20are%20as%20people%2C%20so%20the%20way%20we%20respond%20to%20others%20in%20any%20given%20situation%20can%20alter%20key%20aspects%20of%20someone's%20life%20or%20worldview.%