%2C%20is%20upsetting.%20Face-peeled-from-your-skull%20consideration%20is%20upsetting.%20While%20I%20concede%20to%20imagining%20early%20intervention%20plastic%20surgery%2C%20we%20all%20know%20you%20cannot%20make%20an%2080-year-old%20face%20look%2038.%20You%20just%20can't.%20We%20will%20get%20old.%20We%20will%20lose%20what%20we%20think%20of%20as%20our%20faces%2C%20our%20looks.%20It%20is%20truly%20the%20cost%20of%20life%2C%20and%20of%20living.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b2562dff-7a46-40da-9696-458bdc6f6dd4%5C%22%3EI%20have%20experienced%20more%20now%2C%20and%20it's%20OK%20that%20it%20shows%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20lift%20my%20eyebrows%20and%20consider%20my%20post-eyelid%20lift%20face.%20It's%20more%20open.%20It%20looks%20less%20worn.%20It%20looks%20like%20my%20past.%20It's%20aspirational.%20I%20touch%20the%20few%20gray%20hairs%20and%20consider%20the%20new%20hairstyle%20that%20seems%20to%20be%20emerging.%20I%20consider%20the%20new%20face%20that's%20being%20revealed.%20I%20see%20the%20etches%20of%20my%20strain%2C%20the%20drag%20of%20my%20sorrows.%20When%20I%20tug%20my%20eyebrows%20up%20and%20stretch%20my%20forehead%20closer%20to%20my%20scalp%2C%20I%20attempt%20to%20trick%20my%20brain%20into%20seeing%20a%20different%20past%2C%20less%20effort%2C%20no%20struggle.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it's%20not%20true.%20My%20face%20made%20many%20expressions%2C%20and%20many%20were%20not%20happy%2C%20relaxed%2C%20or%20well-rested.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20may%20yet%20intervene%20on%20my%20face.%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20make%20a%20blanket%20statement%20that%20might%20shift%20as%20time%20passes.%20But%20right%20now%2C%20I'm%20letting%20my%20eyebrows%20rest%20where%20they%20are%2C%20markers%20of%20a%20complex%20life%20of%20depth%2C%20love%2C%20care%2C%20and%20intention.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20am%20not%2027%20anymore.%20I%20am%20more%20able%20to%20love.%20I%20can%20hold%20more.%20My%20younger%20face%20had%20so%20much%20yet%20to%20do%2C%20to%20live%2C%20to%20experience.%20I%20was%20lighter%