-toc-id%3D%5C%22c0e5bf55-e51e-43b8-9fa3-2be10a32f441%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22FAQs%5C%22%3EStomach%20sleeper%20pillow%20FAQs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20type%20of%20pillow%20is%20best%20for%20a%20stomach%20sleeper%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20a%20stomach%20sleeper%2C%20Murray%20recommends%20%26quot%3Bsomething%20soft%20and%20low-profile%20so%20your%20neck%20isn't%20twisted%20all%20night.%26quot%3B%20Consider%20soft%20options%20like%20down%2C%20down%20alternative%2C%20and%20shredded%20memory%20foam%20for%20optimal%20comfort.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EIs%20memory%20foam%20good%20for%20stomach%20sleepers%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMemory%20foam%20contours%20well%20and%20offers%20solid%20support%2C%26quot%3B%20Murray%20said.%20Just%20be%20sure%20that%20your%20memory%20foam%20pillow%20is%20low%20loft%20for%20an%20aligned%20spine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EHow%20thick%20should%20a%20pillow%20be%20for%20stomach%20sleepers%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EStomach%20sleepers%20should%20look%20for%20low-loft%20pillows%2C%20which%20are%20under%20three%20inches%20thick.%20This%20is%20the%20best%20height%20for%20stomach%20sleepers%20to%20avoid%20any%20pain.%20%26quot%3BThe%20right%20pillow%20supports%20deep%2C%20restorative%20sleep%20and%20allows%20you%20to%20wake%20up%20feeling%20refreshed%20and%20ready%20to%20take%20on%20the%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20Murray%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EShould%20stomach%20sleepers%20sleep%20without%20a%20pillow%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EMurray%20said%20stomach%20sleepers%20should%20consider%20skipping%20the%20pillow%20altogether.%20This%20solution%20isn't%20for%20everyone%2C%20though%2C%20especially%20not%20combination%20sleepers%2C%20so%20be%20sure%20to%20try%20it%20out%20before%20tossing%20out%20your%20old%20pillow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-pillows-for-stomach-sleepers%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1754