s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETracking%20snow%20leopards%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20last%20scientific%20survey%20conducted%20through%20camera%20traps%20in%202012%2C%20the%20number%20of%20snow%20leopards%20in%20the%203%2C350%20sq%20km-large%20Hemis%20National%20Park%20stood%20at%2011%2C%20compared%20to%207%20in%202006.%20However%2C%20for%20those%20surveys%2C%20camera%20traps%20were%20only%20installed%20across%20300%20sq%20km.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20now%20in%20the%20process%20of%20completing%20another%20census%20for%20snow%20leopards%20using%20extensive%20camera%20trapping%20methods%20in%20different%20parts%20of%20%3Cstrong%3ELadakh%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20including%20in%20Changthang%2C%20Hemis%20National%20Park%2C%20Kargil%20and%20Nubra%20Valley.%20In%20Hemis%20National%20Park%2C%20we%20have%20about%2060%20snow%20leopards%20today.%20For%20this%20census%20camera%20traps%20were%20installed%20in%20half%20the%20total%20area%20unlike%20in%202006%20and%202012.%20If%20you%20take%20all%20of%20Ladakh%2C%20however%2C%20my%20guess%20is%20that%20the%20figure%20would%20be%20above%20250.%20This%20census%20is%20being%20carried%20out%20under%20the%20guidance%20of%20the%20Wildlife%20Institute%20of%20India.%20The%20results%20of%20this%20census%20may%20come%20by%20the%20end%20of%20this%20year%20or%20early%20next%20year%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWildlife%20guards%20like%20Khenrab%20identify%20areas%20like%20ridgelines%2C%20broken%20cliffs%2C%20deep%20valleys%20and%20hanging%20rocks%20where%20snow%20leopards%20usually%20traverse%2C%20to%20install%20camera%20traps.%20Rolling%20and%20flat%20land%20isn%E2%80%99t%20really%20conducive%20terrain%20for%20the%20snow%20leopard%2C%20although%20for%20this%20census%20camera%20traps%20have%20been%20installed%20in%20not%20so%20conducive%20terrain%20as%20well%2C%20to%20ensure%20that%20none%20are%20missed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%20wp-image-239894%5