%22%3A1754492400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE_11zon-1754293922.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D479520%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22What%20began%20as%20a%20small%20act%20inspired%20by%20a%20neighbour%20became%20a%2025-year-long%20green%20movement.%20With%20no%20funds%20or%20land%2C%20Bholewar%20Palange%20has%20grown%20and%20donated%20over%201%20lakh%20saplings%20%E2%80%94%20turning%20a%20parking%20lot%20into%20a%20thriving%20nursery%20and%20involving%20his%20entire%20family%20in%20the%20mission.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Vidya%20Gowri%20Venkatesh%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F479520%2Fbholeshwar-palange-green-nursery-pune-tata-motors-native-trees-maharashtra-india%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Engineer%20Friends%20Build%20AI-Enabled%20Hydroponic%20Set%20up%20To%20Grow%20Exotic%20Plants%3B%20Earn%20Rs%2050%20Lakh%2FYear%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20interviews%20and%20reporting%20for%20this%20story%20were%20conducted%20in%202024.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20time%20immemorial%2C%20farmers%20have%20relied%20on%20rain%2C%20soil%20fertility%2C%20and%20expensive%20pesticides%20to%20grow%20their%20crops.%20Often%2C%20they%20would%20end%20up%20in%20a%20debt%20trap%20after%20incurring%20huge%20crop%20losses%20owing%20to%20unseasonal%20rains%2C%20hailstorm%2C%20and%20decreasing%20soil%20fertility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20two%20college%20friends%20delved%20into%20this%20sector%20with%20a%20strong%20desire%20to%20revolutionise%20farming%20practices.%20Calvin%20Aranha%20and%20Farish%20Anfal%20have%20integrated%20Artificial%20Intelligence%20(AI)%20into%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F307986%2Fahmedabad-friends-offer-training-earn-crores-with-rise-hydroponics-startup%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehydroponic%20farms%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20grow%20crops!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20their%20vertical%20farm%20in%20Brahmavara%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20they%20are%20growing%20exotic%20crops%20such%20as%20lettuce%2C%20basil%2C%20kale%20and%20parsley%20using%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20after%20completing%20their%20engineering%20at%20the%20Mangalore%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20and%20Engineering%20(MITE)%20in%20Moodabidri%20that%20the%20Udupi-based%20friends%20aspired%20to%20work%20in%20the%20agriculture%20sector.%20Although%20Calvin%20went%20on%20to%20work%20in%20Bengaluru%20in%20the%20corporate%20world%2C%20Farish%20started%20a%20small%20seafood%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20his%20work%2C%20Farish%20says%20he%20learnt%20about%20the%20various%20issues%20faced%20by%20farmers%20at%20the%20grassroots%20level.%20%E2%80%9CI%20found%20that%20farmers%20were%20facing%20a%20lot%20of%20challenges%20in%20making%20farming%20profitable%20due%20to%20climate%20change.%20I%20talked%20to%20more%20farmers%20and%20came%20to%20know%20the%20gravity%20of%20problems%20faced%20by%20them%20on%20a%20regular%20basis%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FKrop-AI-2-1723817299.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Calvin%20and%20Farish%20aimed%20to%20boost%20farmers%E2%80%99%20income%20and%20resilience%20against%20climate%20fluctuations.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FKrop-AI-2-1723817299.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FKrop-AI-2-1723817299-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FKrop-